    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission. The PIV benchmark dataset (vintage 2018) was used to support velocity field validation and is considered representative of the pump geometry flow physics; no re-validation against updated benchmark data was deemed necessary by the assessment team.",
